}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["This class represents a LNK file's TARGET_IDLIST structure. The TARGET_IDLIST structure specifies the target of\nthe link. This information is stored in individual ITEM_ID structures.\n\nArgs:\n    fh: A file-like object to a TARGET_IDLIST structure.\n    size: Size of the TARGET_IDLIST structure"]}, {"name": "dissect.shellitem.lnk.lnk.Lnk", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "dissect.shellitem.lnk.lnk.Lnk.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "fh", "type": {"name": "BufferedReader", "xref": {"fqname": "io.BufferedReader", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "target_idlist", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "LnkTargetIdList", "xref": {"fqname": "dissect.shellitem.lnk.lnk.LnkTargetIdList", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "linkinfo", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "LnkInfo", "xref": {"fqname": "dissect.shellitem.lnk.lnk.LnkInfo", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "stringdata", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "LnkStringData", "xref": {"fqname": "dissect.shellitem.lnk.lnk.LnkStringData", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "extradata", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "LnkExtraData", "xref": {"fqname": "dissect.shellitem.lnk.lnk.LnkExtraData", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "dissect.shellitem.lnk.lnk.Lnk.flag", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "name", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Returns whether supplied flag is set.\n\nArgs:\n    name: Name of the flag\n\nReturns:\n    int: >0 if flag is set"]}, {"name": "dissect.shellitem.lnk.lnk.Lnk._parse_header", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "fh", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "BinaryIO", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.BinaryIO", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "c_lnk.SHELL_LINK_HEADER", "xref": {"fqname": "dissect.shellitem.lnk.c_lnk.c_lnk.SHELL_LINK_HEADER", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": ["Returns LINK header.\n\nParse the header in a buffer that does not start at offset 0\n\nArgs:\n    fh: File object\n\nReturns:\n    LINK header if size is 0x4C, else none"]}, {"name": "dissect.shellitem.lnk.lnk.Lnk.clsid", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "UUID", "xref": {"fqname": "uuid.UUID", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Returns the class id (clsid) of the LNK file."]}, {"name": "dissect.shellitem.lnk.lnk.Lnk.__repr__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["This class represents a LNK file's SHELL_LINK_HEADER, and the remainder of the parsed LNK file structures.\nThis SHELL_LINK_HEADER structure contains identification information, timestamps, and flags that specify the\npresence of optional structures.\n\nParses a .lnk file (aka Microsoft Shell Item) according to the MS-SHLLINK specification\nreference: https://winprotocoldoc.blob.core.windows.net/productionwindowsarchives/MS-SHLLINK/%5bMS-SHLLINK%5d.pdf\n\nArgs:\n    path: (string) Path to a link file.\n    target_idlist: A LnkTargetIdList object.\n    linkinfo: A LnkInfo object.\n    stringdata: A LnkStringData object.\n    extradata: A LnkExtraData object."]}], "exports": []}]}